Description: on uneyed eggs, v. aggressive, bit Herb - beauty!
massive mounds of medium size ones over first half of dive
covered bottom on 2nd half of dive
including one male with about 15 egg masses of all colours on scallop
mixed in with Dodecaceria and small and short

Description: almost all white, the rare orange
some poking out of sandstone holes
including one dead one being eaten by C. oregonensis
